Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.82,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,É?! Đi đi mà! {What? Come on, let's go!}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.82,0:21:33.10,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Thế hai người đang làm gì thế? {So, what are you guys doing?}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.57,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Báo cáo lễ hội. {Festival records.}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.57,0:21:36.28,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Khảo sát hướng nghiệp. {Career consultation survey.}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.44,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Thế tớ đợi đến khi xong nhé! {Then I'll wait for you to finish!}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.44,0:21:42.61,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Tôi có nói là sẽ đi đâu. {I never said I was going.}
